      "content": "thanks. so when you say it failed in places like Iraq, is that because the UN itself is just fundamentally broken/obsolete, or is it just because big countries like the US won't follow the rules? like, is the whole concept of international law even a real thing anymore or is it just a nice idea that doesn't work in reality?",
